        <mxCell id="on_items" value="✓ everything from left PLUS:&#xa;✓ EC2 backend&#xa;✓ EC2 keycloak&#xa;✓ RDS PostgreSQL&#xa;✓ ALB + 2 target groups&#xa;✓ VPC interface endpoints (×5)&#xa;✓ Route 53 A/CNAME records&#xa;✓ CloudFront VPC origin → ALB" style="text;fontSize=10;fillColor=none;strokeColor=none;align=left;" vertex="1" parent="1">
